{{monster info}}

==Useful Info==
'''White imps''' are irritating tier-[[5]] [[demon]]s. Their melee and ranged attacks are all [[cold]]-aligned, but they aren't very strong or dangerous. White imps are often found in or guarding the [[Ice Cave]]s, as well as in [[Cocytus]] and [[the Abyss]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*You can summon your own white imps with the [[Call Imp]] spell. They provide the best ranged firepower of all the possible imps.

==History==
*In [[0.7]], they got [[fire]] vulnerability and [[poison]] resistance.
